press could cause harm to users.","weakness":{"id":53,"name":"Open Redirect"},"original_report_id":null,"original_report_url":null,"attachments":[{"id":83893,"file_name":"wordpress.png","expiring_url":"https://hackerone-us-west-2-production-attachments.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/000/083/893/3af67c05d96f48ad18769e158b8e22306441189d/wordpress.png?response-content-disposition=attachment%3B%20filename%3D%22wordpress.png%22%3B%20filename%2A%3DUTF-8%27%27wordpress.png\u0026response-content-type=image%2Fpng\u0026X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256\u0026X-Amz-Credential=ASIAQGK6FURQROKUBKJA%2F20260429%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request\u0026X-Amz-Date=20260429T101846Z\u0026X-Amz-Expires=3600\u0026X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjECoaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJGMEQCICFzPVBZJi3XHtlDPj7TblatCamktfPrx574nTauylf9AiA3PdkbgAGtRybvhdR0ztl5tGLLxUQuF%2Bh2YQwMyTy4gyq7BQjz%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F8BEAMaDDAxMzYxOTI3NDg0OSIMWFIDUBkHHEafBxpqKo8F4bm6ypVrsq0sQqq7kBz4m%2FmcoJuN7EW1zQ33%2BZjOQeEfsHP5QA0xOJoOpo5gM%2FnZBdSof2Nbw0l5jnxKveTviXuVOV1%2FgWdqIgWuXcc1hSDzS0x%2FCGhSr2P7d9T44cp8Hl9efBscG%2FoxOvZkcws0fC32jrneP6rxMZh9ZIxaGKhIi0DjiOFxE%2FEOTQGgydguefwUJ%2FuLDVVRprlfkIZ6N5%2FesUe5NfOwMAETGLQ3zY0ym0C4gEIe9l82ta3ErvrMqX2HQUoR9ROBzcaOgzMRPeHPjS73qoIsPzq4GVlmn3z42NYbbr0eNLTQRtzbmNIiPRfCR70z21%2BbTpXTcib4eYUqbYzTaRFuHSiOUIuwAiWk3IGyIOmyHgJWAM6GRtO0RAUuCuaoGRdJYZPkWHdxgnqGEvxHMEcCMWptA8ZGoFkXY4Qh0eb8z9ZRIOfrSsitBIzk5Clctw57GvnqLl5De0dQaMQ%2FR3X2D7FieQJAeduhEeZrx43DFEnqfCVlGC4A%2FNYcjZo7A%2F1UmHrIUC2A1PSTC%2FwIcOxXs7RKlJzu3%2BdbNceTIP8SgUz6lGzAugOE1l1OCqSp0zGYpPsS2B4Ph1fOPRq6wzkRmDZwFWiAyBCmOzE21yVOynosKAj4DlhEOslolO5ifa%2Bjma%2Bj1UCWx5EhhaHvWN%2FKBx6qjvuBWRyK9epSyiC5jaANPM96BY8DWT%2Bnao4OEbn6ntetTffCOzxZ%2F79MpT3o0gM6Zbeo8Yqzv%2Br%2BrZUIyBPcCKG%2FKVBc3BfHx%2Bxm7tOtqLOh5LPUun6%2FXuAA0whm%2Fruwd3gfCx5zDbIM8%2Fm60mrNRY4dDhcdkT6%2BaLEYdQf9eBctKAl406OgTK4wIouCQZBhfCH55jCWqsfPBjqyAdUW8GjMM%2FW5hRa%2FeXJjESIUJoh66%2F3cT%2B9HMAlQBtaPXs4alW8esVSHtzcT7qwai5uhMipIVNNNo51tSIzoae4565sUfP%2Bn90cug7nAXAG4jT39mPhrbEh9VIA